<PB REF="019234_0001_0FAA679854D2FA78" MS="y">
<P>SANS SOUCI.</P>
<P>ALIAS FREE and EASY OR AN Evening's Peep into a polite Circle AN INTIRE NEW ENTERTAINMENT:</P>
<P>In THREE ACTS.</P>
<P>BOSTON: PRINTED BY WARDEN AND RUSSELL M,DCC,LXXXV.</P>
</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="dramatis personae">
<PB REF="019234_0002_0FAA67992A9E9948" MS="y">
<HEAD>Dramatis Per&s;onae.</HEAD>
<LIST>
<HEAD>MEN.</HEAD>
<ITEM>Mr. IMPORTANCE,</ITEM>
<ITEM>JEMMY SATIRIST,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Doctor GALLANT,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Mr. BON TON,</ITEM>
<ITEM>YOUNG FORWARD,</ITEM>
<ITEM>LITTLE PERT.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Waiter, Servants, &amp;c.</HI></ITEM>
</LIST>
